sentences.english: The last chapter gives an indication of the state-of-the-art in an industrial environment.

sentences.english: That's according to a new AP Ipsos poll.

sentences.chinese: 目的阐述恶唑烷酮类抗菌药物的最新研究进展。

sentences.english: Now the latest intelligence evaluations were being announced worldwide, nearly in real time.
sentences.chinese: 现在最新的情报分析实时地向全世界公布。

sentences.english: State-of-the-art systems report producing biogas that is more than 95% pure methane.
sentences.chinese: 最新系统报告产生的沼气中甲烷的含量超过95%。

sentences.english: In this paper, the newest developing of plastic optical fiber is reviewed for various communication.
sentences.chinese: 本文综述了各种通信用塑料光纤研究的最新进展。

sentences.english: This new technology is sure to make waves in the cellular phone.
sentences.chinese: 最新的科技一定会在手机的领域中造成哄动。

sentences.english: You are responsible for sustaining well-informed and motivated Rotary clubs.
sentences.chinese: 您有责任提供最新的资讯并激励著扶轮社。

sentences.chinese: 详细介绍了血液透析机的组成原理及最新进展。

sentences.english: Saturn's newest addition could explain how Cassini Regio came to be.

sentences.english: The latest video games are simply stunning.
sentences.chinese: 最新的视频游戏简直让人难以置信。

sentences.english: Scroll down to read about the latest update, or just click here.
sentences.chinese: 滚动鼠标向下，阅读最新的更新，或者点击这里。

sentences.english: He was well informed and updated with all kinds of current affairs.
sentences.chinese: 他见多识广，并且了解各种最新的时事新闻。

sentences.english: Include the latest edition of the local paper, magazines that might be of interest or your local “What’s Up?

sentences.chinese: 本课程介绍了物流业的最新技术和发展。

sentences.english: He reordered two pairs of black leather shoes of the latest type.
sentences.chinese: 他又订购了两双最新式的黑皮鞋。
